meta {
  name: Opt out of Okta user communication emails
  type: http
  seq: 3
}

post {
  url: {{orgUrl}}/api/v1/org/privacy/oktaCommunication/optOut
  body: none
  auth: none
}

headers {
  Accept: application/json
  Authorization: SSWS {{apiKey}}
}

docs {
Opts out all users of this org from Okta communication emails

**Responses:**
- `200`: Success
- `403`: 
